  "text": "This multitargeted antifolate is unique among the folate antagonists to inhibit at least three different enzymes in the folate pathway: thymidylate synthase (TS), dihydrofolate reductase (DHFR) and glycinamide ribonucleotide formyl transferase (GARFT) [CITATION_1] .",
